WEBVTT

1
00:51:48.220 --> 00:51:49.410 
是的  我认为是的
Yes, I should think you are.

2
00:51:49.410 --> 00:51:51.470 
我不要被这样操纵
I will not be manipulated like this.

3
00:51:51.470 --> 00:51:52.580 
好  约翰
Fine. John?

4
00:51:53.280 --> 00:51:54.150 
约翰
John!

5
00:51:55.360 --> 00:51:58.570 
我觉得我见过这种枪  水牛步枪
Yeah, I think I've seen one of these. It's a buffalo gun.

6
00:51:58.570 --> 00:52:03.020 
20世纪40年代的  老式瞄准镜  没有准星
I'd say 1940s, old-fashioned sight. No crosshairs.

7
00:52:03.490 --> 00:52:07.030 
眼镜  眼镜  内森戴眼镜
Glasses, glasses. Nathan wears glasses.

8
00:52:07.200 --> 00:52:09.150 
埃文斯在三百米远处被射杀
Evans was shot from 300 metres.

9
00:52:09.340 --> 00:52:11.730 
这种口径枪的后坐力
The kickback from a gun with this calibre...

10
00:52:14.970 --> 00:52:16.040 
会很强
...would be massive.

11
00:52:17.220 --> 00:52:18.950 
没有伤口  没有伤疤
No cuts, no scarring.

12
00:52:19.050 --> 00:52:20.420 
不是内森  下一个是谁
It's not Nathan, then. Who's next?

13
00:52:20.420 --> 00:52:22.600 
做得好  华生医生  你真是有用
Well done, Dr Watson. How useful you are.

